title: The Vision - Part 1 (EN short version)
description:
Dear pirates of the world,
I was told this story by Matthew, a Visitor from the Future. Inventor of a revolutionary technology : "The Jump in Time". He made "the Jump" just before the terrible events that have befallen his country and devastated his people.
This story contains information on the Future, such as business secrets, political anticipation and stuff....Be careful who you give this book to. 
I did the best I could for you to transcribe it
